OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FWelsh Liberal Democrats are vowing to
OL,8,Fput "turning the NHS around" at the
OL,9,Fheart of their campaign for the Senedd
OL,10,Felection in May.
OL,12,FMembers of the party are meeting in
OL,13,FCardiff ahead of their annual
OL,14,Fconference and with just two months to
OL,15,Fgo until an election that is shaping
OL,16,Fup to be the most significant in a
OL,17,Fgeneration.
OL,19,FAt a pre-conference rally on Friday,
OL,20,Fthe leader, Jane Dodds, arrived in an
OL,21,Fambulance to highlight the issue.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@\O]
