OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FShe's also expected to use her
OL,8,Fconference speech to focus on the same
OL,9,Fmessage.
OL,11,FThe leader has previously said that
OL,12,Fher party's other priorities are
OL,13,F"social care, free child care,
OL,14,Fcleaning up Wales' rivers and a 'Green
OL,15,FDeal' for young people."
OL,17,FThe Lib Dems are also committed to
OL,18,Fusing the Welsh Government's powers to
OL,19,Fraise part of income tax in order to
OL,20,Ffind more money for those priorities.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
