OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FMs Dodds told this week's Sharp End
OL,8,Fprogramme that "We've passed a policy
OL,9,Falready, the opposite of the
OL,10,FConservatives, a penny on Welsh income
OL,11,Ftax rates if we can't get the money
OL,12,Ffrom elsewhere."
OL,14,FIt's also clear that the Lib Dems will
OL,15,Ffocus much of their fire on Plaid
OL,16,FCymru's and the Green Party's support
OL,17,Findependence for Wales.
OL,26,@pD@POUtD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
