OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772831519
OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FMs Dodds has previously said that "The
OL,8,FWelsh Liberal Democrats are clear: we
OL,9,Fwill not support any government,
OL,10,Fformally or informally, that spends a
OL,11,Fsingle pound on independence."
OL,13,FThat red line could prove to be
OL,14,Fpivotal in the days, weeks and months
OL,15,Ffollowing May's election. No party is
OL,16,Flikely to win a majority to govern
OL,17,Falone and will have to reach deals
OL,18,Fwith others in order to pass budgets
OL,19,Fand major legislation.
OL,26,@oD@cOUsD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
