PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772831519
OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FAs the only Lib Dem member of the
OL,8,FSenedd, Jane Dodds has shown a
OL,9,Fwillingness to reach deals, most
OL,10,Frecently allowing the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment's 2025 budget to pass in
OL,12,Fexchange for extra spending
OL,13,Fcommitments on social care, councils
OL,14,Fand support for a ban on greyhound
OL,15,Fracing.
OL,17,FLib Dems in the past have joined
OL,18,Fformal coalitions, with Labour in the
OL,19,FSenedd in the early 2000s and with the
OL,20,FConservatives in Westminster after
OL,21,F2010.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
