OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772831519
OL,3,CWelsh Lib Dems say NHS will be at the
OL,4,Cheart of their bid to win Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThat latter experience still scars
OL,8,Fmany members' memories, not the least
OL,9,Fbecause it led to a collapse in votes
OL,10,Fafter 2015 that swept up the party
OL,11,Fhere in Wales.
OL,13,FNow Jane Dodds is hoping for company
OL,14,Fin the Senedd after May, but the polls
OL,15,Faren't particularly encouraging.
OL,17,FThe most recent poll for ITV Cymru
OL,18,FWales, in January, showed the Lib Dems
OL,19,Fwinning 5% of the vote, a figure that
OL,20,Fcould result in just three of the 96
OL,21,Fseats available in the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
